# DM Mono — articles section only

DM Mono (`DMMono_400Regular`, `DMMono_500Medium`) is **exclusively** for the ARTICLES / receipt UI in transaction detail (`app/transaction-detail.tsx` — `TransactionReceiptCard`, itemized line amounts).

## Everywhere else

- Labels → Inter (`interMediumText`, `typographyKit`, etc.)
- Money amounts → `moneyAmountTypography()` (Inter ExtraBold) from `apps/mobile/constants/theme.ts`

## Bad — do not use DM Mono here

- Dashboard / Accueil (`app/(tabs)/index.tsx`)
- `BankAccountCard`, `CashAccountCard`, `LoanCard`
- `TransactionRow` and other list rows
- Debt, cash, portfolio, chart metrics

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — DM Mono on dashboard or cards
fontFamily: 'DMMono_500Medium'
import { ARTICLES_MONO_FONT } from '@/constants/theme' // in DashboardStatCard

// ✅ GOOD — Inter ExtraBold for amounts
import { moneyAmountTypography } from '@/constants/theme'
style={moneyAmountTypography({ tier: 'stat' })}
```

## Good — articles section only

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD — transaction-detail ARTICLES / receipt lines only
import { ARTICLES_MONO_FONT, articlesReceiptTypography } from '@/constants/theme'
style={articlesReceiptTypography('medium')}
```

Reference tokens: `ARTICLES_MONO_FONT`, `articlesReceiptTypography()`, `moneyAmountTypography()` in `apps/mobile/constants/theme.ts`.
